reviewText: Max and Ruby are always fun to watch and very educational too. We even find ourselves watching these wonderful video's.
My grandson loves Max and Ruby. He watches them so much, they are worn out and I have to buy more. Good and fast service.
Expected better, but my son is a huge Max and Ruby Fan.  The best part is leaving a required number of words in the description, like an essay or something.

This movie also has other shows on it as well and I bought it to show at my son's 3 year birthday party coming up. We are going to play pin the tail on Max game and watch Max's birthday episode. Thanks.
